def numberOfPatterns(m, n):
    skip = [[0] * 10 for _ in range(10)]
    skip[1][7] = skip[7][1] = 5
    skip[1][3] = skip[3][1] = 2
    skip[3][9] = skip[9][3] = 6
    skip[7][9] = skip[9][7] = 8
    skip[1][9] = skip[9][1] = skip[2][8] = skip[8][2] = skip[3][7] = skip[7][3] = skip[4][6] = skip[6][4] = 5
    visit = [False] * 10
    ans = 0
    for l in range(m, n + 1):
        ans += dfs(visit, skip, 1, l - 1) * 4
        ans += dfs(visit, skip, 2, l - 1) * 4
        ans += dfs(visit, skip, 5, l - 1)
    return ans

def dfs(visit, skip, cur, remain):
    if remain < 0:
        return 0
    if remain == 0:
        return 1
    visit[cur] = True
    ans = 0
    for i in range(1, 10):
        if not visit[i] and (skip[cur][i] == 0 or visit[skip[cur][i]]):
            ans += dfs(visit, skip, i, remain - 1)
    visit[cur] = False
    return ans
